description:
When it comes to Bible prophecy, people like to focus on the Antichrist and the mark of the beast and try to figure out their identities. But without the false prophet, there is no mark of the beast. Who is the false prophet that is so intimately connected with the beast system?

In this episode the identity of the false prophet in the book of Revelation is explained. Learn why the rise of the false prophet is one of the surest signs of the Antichrist. Matthew Schanche and MacKenzie Drebit reveal the identifying features of the false prophet in this Revelation Bible study.

#truthmatters #prophecy #vatican #revelation 

1:35 What Revelation says about the false prophet. Key driver of the mark and image of the beast. Identifying features.
6:20 The false prophet is the same as the second beast of Revelation 13. How we know this is true.
10:27 Examination of Revelation 13 for details on the false prophet.
12:45 The deadly wound of the first beast. Pinpointing the time that the second beast rises.
14:48 List: Summary of 8 characteristics of second beast/false prophet.
17:00 Study of each of the characteristics. Two horns, lamb-like.
18:49 Speaks like a dragon.
20:02 Same power as the first beast. Why the false prophet cannot be a single individual.
24:10 Causes the earth to worship the first beast.
27:05 Miracles to deceive.
27:44 It will use its power to make an image. The mark of the beast cant happen until the false prophet sets up the image to the beast.
30:18 Who is the false prophet? Testing the contenders against the qualifying characteristics.
37:32 What does Satan want? Whats the end goal? Study of Matthew 4. Purpose of the new world order.
42:10 Compare Satans goals with goals of the beast and false prophet. The single goal uniting the behind-the-scenes players identified.
43:55 Defining wonders.
45:58 What the image of the beast is. How Lauren Boeberts statements affirm this interpretation. How the image defines the mark of the beast.
49:07 Gallup poll showing decline in faith in Gods Word in America. How will US go from secular state to hardcore Christian nation? The catalyst.
53:07 Great Controversy on agents of Satan. Why the world, including atheists, will be deceived into worshiping the beast. The only thing that will protect us from deception.
57:13 The war between Satan and the remnant. There will be only two camps. Qualifying attributes of the remnant.
